title: In case of development of the plot reserved for Public Open Spaces under AR as per Serial No
clause_text: In case of development of the plot reserved for Public Open Spaces under AR as per Serial No. 15, 16 & 48 & 49 of Table No 5, the provisions of Regulation No.27 may not be insisted.
